body_html: Sorry you're having trouble. Did you previously install another version of tensorflow? If so, you must use pip uninstall to remove the first installation before trying to upgrade. If you have an unusual linux distribution it may be necessary to install from sources by configuring and compiling on your machine.

body: Sorry you're having trouble.  Did you previously install another version of tensorflow?  If so, you must use pip uninstall to remove the first installation before trying to upgrade.
